## Workflow

```
session_start → read instructions → select task → execute → verify → handoff
```

### Before You Start

1. Run `session_start(".")` to get context and pending tasks
2. Read this file and applicable skills
3. Review last handoff and progress log

### During Work

1. Check scope before editing: `scope_check(".", "path/to/file")`
2. Make changes incrementally
3. Log progress: `progress_log(".", { summary: "...", status: "in-progress" })`

### Before Finishing

1. Run `verify_run(".")` — all steps must pass
2. Call `session_handoff(...)` with summary, unfinished items, and next steps

